'''Cybernetic psychosis''' was a condition that could occur in [[Cyborg/Legends|cyborgs]] using [[Brain/Legends|brain]]-altering [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetic]] implants or borg constructs. The cyborg's mind lost the ability to maintain control of the cybernetic [[Computer/Legends|computer]], driving them insane.<ref name="NEGWT">''[[The New Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref> 

A cyborg [[Unidentified cyborg pilot|pilot]] suffered from cybernetic psychosis, causing insanity and the belief that a [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunter]] piloted by [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] was the prototype ''[[Onyx Star]]''. The pilot believed that he had been contracted by the [[Tenloss Syndicate/Legends|Tenloss Syndicate]] to prevent its delivery to the [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]].<ref name="Crystal">{{GamerCite|5|The Crystal}}</ref>

